class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Schematic overview 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Real example 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-4DA554EF-9005-4DFC-80DB-FDC608C268D3" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-9B81451A-ACCF-46A0-A4EA-CE6AAB05CBA5-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9B81451A-ACCF-46A0-A4EA-CE6AAB05CBA5-low.png"/></fig></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-801751CF-18EE-4685-865F-8F4357D56C80" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-E24BF08B-1908-4492-BE46-84392D372433-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E24BF08B-1908-4492-BE46-84392D372433-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-EC1EAE23-40EC-4B10-A2C9-83873F76DC70" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Symptoms</b> 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Lower OD (optical density) than expected 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Non-uniform OD 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Patterns visible in both Carriage and Media direction 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Only visible in gloss modes. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Mainly visible in areas that have low ink coverage 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Functional logging (if available)</b>
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No logging available which can pinpoint to this case.
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ADAM-triggers</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No ADAM triggers are available 
</p></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-20E8BDA6-309C-4B23-A03D-10A5D2890BB5" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-874E6F4A-7A0A-4C87-83B1-295E5945B5D4-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-874E6F4A-7A0A-4C87-83B1-295E5945B5D4-svg.svg"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BB9BDDD1-E29C-42C5-BF10-2854E3AE4223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Steps explanation</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D963269B-E108-446A-A212-4581FEAA8740" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="30*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">To do 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check whether correct profile is selected.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Download correct profile.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The profile can be downloaded from: 
<xref href="https://graphiplaza.cpp.canon/media/" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>https://graphiplaza.cpp.canon/media/</xref> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lowering temperature of platen.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">In some cases lowering the platen temperature might improve spreading on the media 
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-2513E5DF-C282-453D-9841-6E539DB0EB51" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Evaluate/Prevention</title><p class="- topic/p ">Do not use gloss mode on low spreading media. In case a profile for this media is available please download it from: 
<xref href="https://graphiplaza.cpp.canon/media/" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>https://graphiplaza.cpp.canon/media/</xref>. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-987F83F9-80F0-41BC-B82B-BB16DA268203" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Background info</title><p class="- topic/p ">Some slow spreading media is not suitable for gloss-mode. In most cases these kind of media is still capable for making good prints in matt-mode. This is caused by the fact ink needs to spread over the media to get a uniform inklayer. In gloss modes the time between placing the ink on the media and curing is larger than in matt-modes. In case of slow spreading media the impact of the surface of the media is higher in gloss modes. As in lower coverage the amount of spreading is more critical than a high coverage this artifact is mostly visible in lower coverage areas 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the media is not spreading well the texture of the media might also get visible.
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-945E6C60-1212-47DF-9487-92374227D4B4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Solutions</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
